MyTest.java is the junit that can produce the exception&lt;br/&gt;
MyTestOuput.txt is the output of schema.toString()&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12935559" author="cutting" created="Wed, 24 Nov 2010 22:59:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a patch that should fix this, including a unit test.&lt;/p&gt;

